            S2 --> T2{2B Complete?}
        end

        T1 & T2 -->|Yes| U[Begin Phase 3]

        subgraph PHASE3["Phase 3: Guidance Repair Loop Verification"]
            U --> V1["Spawn teacher-update-guidance"]

