        end

        V4 -->|Yes| W[Begin Phase 4]

        subgraph PHASE4["Phase 4: Testing Validation"]
            W --> X1[Spawn test-guidance-simulator]

            %% DECISION: Use test-guidance-simulator for end-to-end validation
